  Would you like to create a new workspace?
  <span class="info-text-tip simptip-position-right simptip-multiline simptip-smooth" data-tooltip="Do you want to use a class of encompass users? If not you can match by just username or enter a plain text name">
    <i class="fas fa-info-circle info-icon"></i>
  </span>
</p>
{{radio-group options=createWs selectedValue=selectedValue}}

